{"履修期": "春学期", "主な教授言語": "英語", "授業目的": "This course is designed to help students understand the fundamentals of formal debate.", "到達目標": "At the end of this course, students will be able to do the following:1. Clearly state an opinion2. Coherently explain an opinion3. Support an opinion 4. Organize an opinion into a speech5. Refute an opinion 6. Challenge an opposing opinion 7. Debate an opinion This course will also help students to become more mature, confident public speakers. When learning to debate, students will also develop their skills in speaking, listening, writing, reading, researching, critical thinking, discussing, collaborative learning, and much more.", "特記事項": "", "関連科目": "", "授業の概要・背景": "", "授業方法": "Lectures will be given to introduce the fundamentals of debate. Students will then work on assignments that will help them practice and review each major part of a formal debate. Audio-visual materials will be presented to students in preparation for their own final debates.", "トピック": {"第1回": ["<div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm;font-size:medium;font-family:Cambria,serif;\"><span lang=\"JA\" ms=\"ms\" mincho\";\"=\"mincho';'\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:;\">【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:;\">Startup Week</span><span lang=\"JA\" ms=\"ms\" mincho\";\"=\"mincho';'\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:;\">】リンク：https://kwanseio365-my.sharepoint.com/:f:/g/personal/ftp47898_nuc_kwansei_ac_jp/IgCHsV7RrZ4pS5_C91w1bkYgAThkhXEeiBEJlhfc3iYITys?e=MCs9Yp</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm;font-size:medium;font-family:Cambria,serif;\"><span lang=\"JA\" ms=\"ms\" mincho\";\"=\"mincho';'\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:;\">(Complete the handout to the best of your ability from pages 1-3 and have it with you when we meet on April 13.)&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm;font-size:medium;font-family:Cambria,serif;\